The French 1986 current account balance payment surplus revise slightly upwards 25.8 billion franc 25.4 billion franc figure announce month Finance Ministry said. This compare 1.5 billion deficit 1985 surplus 1979 substantially low 50 billion surplus forecast previous socialist government lose office March year. Net long-term capital outflow rise sharply 70.5 billion franc 8.8 billion 1985 largely due major foreign debt repayment ministry said. In fourth quarter alone unadjusted surplus rise 14.1 billion franc 6.6 billion previous quarter adjust surplus fell 7.4 billion 9.1 billion. Fourth quarter medium long-term foreign debt repayment exceed credit 11 billion francs. REUTER 